headline: Perrigo (PRGO) Down 9.7% Since Last Earnings Report: Can It Rebound?

headline: SCCM Enhanced Equity Income Fund Sold Baxter Int’l (BAX) Due to Near-Term Headwinds
summary: Cullen Capital Management, LLC, operating under the name Schafer Cullen Capital Management, Inc. (SCCM), has released its “SCCM Enhanced Equity Income Fund” third-quarter investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. US equities continued to rise in the third quarter, with the S&P 500 returning 8.1% while the Russell 1000 Value was up 5.3%. […]
